<font color="#FF0000">WE WERE THERE</font><br>
<tt>Sun Jan 11 21:03:14 US/Eastern 1998
</tt><p>
Jed,<br><br>
You said  &quot;We had a secret war in Cambodia that we did not admit to and in fact denied.&quot;<br><br>
I am one of the guys that was there and no for a fact we were in Cambodia.  I saw and heard most things.  I observed fighter attacks and B-52 bombings raids in Cambodia.  I listened on open Mike to the relentless 24 hour per day weapon fire.  We worked the Iron Triangle deep into the Cambodian jungles.<br><br>
When the War terminated in Vietnam we were sent to continue in Cambodia.  There is no doubt that we were there.<br><br>

